title: Emperor of the North (1973)
description:
Set in the mid-30's Oregon, Emperor of the North is a classic hoboe / railroad film directed by the great and late Robert Aldrich. Fabulous music by Frank DeVol, too!


Starring: Lee Marvin, Ernest Borgnine, Keith Carradine, Charles Tyner and others.
